WEBVTT

00:01.734 --> 00:04.536
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.604 --> 00:07.039
                     E-leven and
                        holding.

00:07.107 --> 00:08.073
  Hey, that's a personal best.  

00:08.141 --> 00:09.074
                         Uh-huh.

00:09.175 --> 00:10.142
        What's going on?        

00:10.210 --> 00:11.176
                 We're trying to
                  count how many

00:11.244 --> 00:12.611
                 Spanish peanuts
                    Cliff can...

00:12.746 --> 00:14.480
                fit up his nose.

00:14.547 --> 00:15.748
                      (nasally):
                        And, uh,

00:15.882 --> 00:16.815
    11's the limit.             

00:16.883 --> 00:18.350
  I know my nostrils.           

00:19.853 --> 00:21.453
     Let's see, now, who had 11?

00:21.521 --> 00:22.621
              Uh, Norm Peterson.

00:22.689 --> 00:23.689
            Hey.                
                        Oh, yes,

00:23.757 --> 00:25.657
                I know Cliffie's
                    nostrils.   

00:25.725 --> 00:26.658
Here you go, Norm.              

00:26.726 --> 00:29.028
                      Thank you.
     Cliff, are you crazy?      

00:29.095 --> 00:31.096
  You've really been stuffing   
     peanuts up your nose?      

00:31.164 --> 00:32.531
    That's dangerous.           

00:32.598 --> 00:35.501
You could puncture your sinuses,
 you can even get brain damage. 

00:35.568 --> 00:37.336
 Oh, come on, I've been doing   
 this kind of stuff for years.  

00:37.404 --> 00:38.570
 It's no big deal.              

00:38.638 --> 00:42.408
             Yeah, Cliffie, but,
          uh, but never 11, pal.

00:42.475 --> 00:44.176
 Uh, yeah,                      
 you're right, Norm.            

00:44.244 --> 00:45.511
 Uh, hey,                       
 uh, Rebecca,                   

00:45.578 --> 00:46.745
 I'm gonna mosey                
 into the poolroom              

00:46.813 --> 00:47.913
 and, uh,                       
 pry some of these out.         

00:47.981 --> 00:49.314
 Give me the corkscrew,         
 will you?                      

00:50.350 --> 00:52.851
            Thank you.          

00:54.988 --> 00:56.989
Hey, Norm, that's quite a little
 sum of money you've got there. 

00:57.057 --> 00:57.990
                Yeah, well...   

00:58.058 --> 00:59.391
Maybe you'd like                
to apply                        

00:59.559 --> 01:00.592
 some of this to your bar tab.  

01:00.660 --> 01:01.694
                      (laughing)

01:03.863 --> 01:04.897
            That's very good.   

01:04.964 --> 01:06.031
        (chuckles)              

01:06.099 --> 01:07.366
                You know, you're
        starting to fit in here.

01:07.434 --> 01:08.701
                That's great.   

01:08.768 --> 01:10.703
      (theme song begins)       

01:14.874 --> 01:17.176
    ¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶      

01:17.243 --> 01:20.346
¶ Takes everything you've got ¶ 

01:20.413 --> 01:23.015
        ¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶     

01:23.083 --> 01:26.485
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

01:26.553 --> 01:30.389
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

01:31.458 --> 01:33.926
  ¶ Sometimes you want to go ¶  

01:33.993 --> 01:38.430
    ¶ Where everybody           
    knows your name ¶           

01:39.733 --> 01:44.336
      ¶ And they're always      
        glad you came ¶         

01:44.404 --> 01:46.605
         ¶ You wanna be         
      where you can see ¶       

01:46.673 --> 01:49.174
         ¶ Our troubles         
    are all the same ¶          

01:49.242 --> 01:53.445
      ¶ You wanna be where      
  everybody knows your name ¶   

01:54.714 --> 01:56.648
         ¶ You wanna go         
      where people know ¶       

01:56.716 --> 01:59.885
  ¶ People are all the same ¶   

01:59.953 --> 02:04.523
      ¶ You wanna go where      
  everybody knows your name. ¶  

